- [ ] Current mode is clearly indicated
- [ ] Touch target is 44x44px minimum
- [ ] Works on mobile devices
- [ ] Keyboard accessible (Tab, Enter, Arrow keys)
- [ ] Screen reader announces mode changes

## Definition of Done

